name: Chrysanthemum
description:
Joy, Optimism, Perfection
Romance and sophistication wrapped in one. This bra is lined with 4 rows of clear swarovski crystals on the bottom lining of the bra with a pink ribbon lined directional on top. The top of the bra is lined with pink lace and a white ribbon along the top. This bra is an extreme push up with padding to model to your body. Perfect for any night out or in.

name: Eglantine
description:
Poetry
These hand made flowers accent this bustier like no other with the smaller ones having a flawless crystal swarovski flathead and the larger ones have a gorgeous swarovski pendent in the middle with pearl accents down the bust and middle boning. Color changes for petals and pearls are listed below. Bustier has a demi lining and steel boning for great lift.

name: Mallow
description:
Sweetness, delicate beauty
Two different patterns on each bust both made from gold, brass, and gunmetal studs. Made to give the eyes an illusion. One bust has the pattern of two rows of each individual color and the other bust creating a zig zag line across the bust. This bra is an extreme push up with padding to model to your body. Perfect for any night out or in.

name: Daisy
description:
Beauty, innocence, loyal love, purity
This bustier is everything you need and everything you want!! With its eye popping design, this bustier is the life of the party.  Please choose colors of studs from the list below. Bustiers are a satin material, cropped top and demi bust.

name: Snowdrop
description:
Consolation hope
Hand braided ribbon lining the bra with clear swarovski crystals accenting center of bra, white ribbon lining top of bra with swarovski rhinestones layed directly on top. Color of ribbon can be changed chose three colors only for bottom three ribbons (solid colors only) This bra is an extreme push up with padding to model to your body. Perfect for any night out or in.

name: Tulip
description:
Fame, Perfect lover, Declaration of Love, Believe Me, Hopeless Love
Rainbow studded bra is a real eye catcher with three rows of each color going from red all the way to white, think of the rainbow. This bra is an extreme push up with padding to model to your body. Perfect for any night out or in.

name: Rose
description:
Passion, Love, Desire, Purity
Hand laced with pink lace between boning and along bust of bustier. Two rows of swarovski crystal rhinestone accent the top of bust with an array of multi colored swarovski crystals along bust. Bustier has a demi lining and steel boning for great lift.

name: Sunflower
description:
Pride, adoration
Body, Body, Body. This bra is all about the body with a gorgeous body chain extending from the bra accented with spikes and studs to complete the piece. Please pick one color for the chain, spikes and studs check the colors tab for the available colors. This bra is an extreme push up with padding to model to your body. Perfect for any night out or in.

name: Ivy
description:
Affection, friendship, fidelity, wedded love
A personal favorite with our designer this buster is tons of fun wit the color of the bustier being interchangeable from white or black you can create the look you want with the multi colored swarovski crystals covering the bust and creating a fun pattern along the body of the bustier. Bustier has a demi lining and steel boning for great lift.

name: Lily
description:
Purity of heart, majesty and honor
Flawless, fierce a bold statement is made with this bra, accented with crystal swarovski rhinestone flatbacks and completing this look with spikes and studs. The colors of the crystal swarovski rhinestone flatbacks can be changed with any of the colors listed. Please choose one color for the studs and spikes from the color tab. This bra is an extreme push up with padding to model to your body. Perfect for any night out or in.

name: Violet
description:
Love, Faithfulness, Watchfulness
Fabulous bustier with teal rose petals along the bust and pink ribbon along the boning with the additional detail of white lace along the bottom. Bustier has a demi lining and steel boning for great lift.

name: Marigold
description:
Sorrow, jealousy, caress, pretty love, affection, sacred
Out of this world bra. Made with a fabulous black bra, hand painted for that authentic galaxy feel and glow in the dark painted stars with crystal swaroski accents. This bra is an extreme push up with padding to model to your body. Perfect for any night out or in.

name: Carnation
description:
Aching heart, admiration
Completely laced with a gorgeous pink lace and a simple white lace trim at the top of the bra. Accented with two rows of pearls hanging down from the bra and a large bow in the middle. Color combinations for the pearls can be changed with any of the colors listed. Color of bow can be changed with any solid color of your choice. This bra is an extreme push up with padding to model to your body. Perfect for any night out or in.

name: Wallflower
description:
Lasting beauty, fidelity
Beautiful bustier, accented with a darling tulle flower in the middle of the bust with silver buttons attached. Color of flower can be chosen from any solid color. With gorgeous brass studs along the top lining of the bust and the waist of the bustier. Bustiers are a satin material, cropped top and demi bust.

name: Orchid
description:
Mature charm, Beauty, Love
Glamours bra with satin ribbon sewn into the bra in an arrow formation on one bust with flirty ribbon on the sides of each bust. Please chose color of ribbons from list below, limit colors to two. This bra is an extreme push up with padding to model to your body. Perfect for any night out or in.

name: Daffodile
description:
Respect, sunshine, unrequited love, regard
This is where it all started. The first creation our designer Elizabeth created. Randomly scattered along the bust and body of the bustier using circular gunmetal studs and having a pairing of feathers along the middle of the body. Color of feathers can be changed with colors listed below, only chose two. Bustier has a demi lining and steel boning for great lift.

name: Water Lily
description:
Purity of heart, growing indifference, eloquence
Hand braided ribbon completely lining bust accompanied by an eye popping colored ribbon lining the to trim as well as the middle area of the bra. Clear swarovski crystals line bottom edge of bra. Please choose two different colors for ribbon at checkout (solid colors only). This bra is an extreme push up with padding to model to your body. Perfect for any night out or in.

name: Dog Rose
description:
Pleasure and Pain
Charismatic, elegant, sophistication. Just a few words to describe this beautiful piece, white lace along the top of the bust with swarovski rhinestones lining the boning and gunmetal studs on both sides of the swarovski rhinestones. Bustier has a demi lining and steel boning for great lift.

name: Lilac
description:
Pride, beauty
Made for the boldest raves with yellow pearl beads lining the bust with an accent of pink ribbon lining the pearl beads. Accompanied by a gorgeous ruffle going along the bottom to the top of the bra. This bra is an extreme push up with padding to model to your body. Perfect for any night out or in.

name: Jasmine
description:
Love, attachment, sensuality, elegance, grace, modesty
The simplest design can make the boldest statements. This design focuses on the structure of the bustier with square studs along the bust and circular studs along the boning. Bustier has a demi lining and steel boning for great lift.

name: Hollyhock
description:
Fruitfulness
Adorable bra with accents of multi colored aluminum roses and neutral colored pearl acrylic flatback beads. Avaliable with the sweetest sequence bow in the middle, please choose a color from the list below. This bra is an extreme push up with padding to model to your body. Perfect for any night out or in.

name: Buttercup
description:
Riches, Childishness
Simple and elegant bustier. Bust completely lined with gunmetal circular studs.  Bustier has a demi lining and steel boning for great lift.

name: Holly
description:
Am I forgotten, domestic happiness, defense
Punk rock bra with studded pattern on base of bra with alternating colors of studs. Please choose two colors for studs from the list below. This bra is an extreme push up with padding to model to your body. Perfect for any night out or in.

name: Peach Blossom
description:
I am your captive
Gorgeous bra accented with silver studs along the top of the bust with two colored feathers along four points on the bra. Please choose two colors for the feathers from any colors listed. This bra is an extreme push up with padding to model to your body. Perfect for any night out or in.

name: Almond Blossom
description:
Symbolizing hope, delicacy, sweetness
Gorgeous white bra with white ruffle ribbon accenting the bust of the bra with mutli color shades of pink acrylic pearl flatback beads lining the top and center of the bra as well as an accent of sea green acrylic pearl flatback beads. This bra is an extreme push up with padding to model to your body. Perfect for any night out or in.

name: Iris
description:
Flame, passion hope, faith, wisdom
Bold bra with gold studs creating two different patterns on each bust with one pattern creating a pyramid shape and the other completely lining the outside of the bust. This bra is an extreme push up with padding to model to your body. Perfect for any night out or in.
